# Rust build artifacts
/target

# Release packaging artifacts. CI generates these in the workspace root
# (Compress-Archive on Windows, tar czf on Unix) before uploading them
# to the GitHub release. Local repro of the packaging step would
# otherwise leave these in the repo root and tempt accidental `git add`.
/local-llm-acp-*.zip
/local-llm-acp-*.tar.gz

# Per-user lockfiles for binaries are committed (Cargo.lock is tracked) but
# editor / debugger swap files are not.
*.swp
*.swo

# IDE state
/.idea/
/.vscode/

# Council / verification artifacts — research reports, council outputs, fetched
# primary sources used to audit the shim. Local-only; do not ship in the repo.
/reports/

# Campaign planning scratch — council briefs, todo checklists, lessons captures,
# synthetic test payloads. Local-only; the durable campaign output (runbooks,
# results) lives in /docs/ instead.
/tasks/

# Obsolete RunPod-era infrastructure left behind after the local-Blackwell
# pivot. Kept gitignored rather than deleted so the operator can choose when
# to remove it from their working tree.
/docker/

# Stray Windows file-metadata directories that Windows file ops occasionally
# leave behind in the working tree. Never useful in a Rust crate.
/Microsoft/

# Python bytecode caches from campaign scripts. Never tracked.
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# OS junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Internal-only docs — engineering handoffs, threat models, roadmaps, and
# investigation briefs that reference the private nwiro codebase. Never publish;
# they live in the private working repo only. Guarded here so an accidental
# `git add docs` cannot re-introduce them into the public snapshot.
/docs/FINAL-PUBLISH-TEST-PLAN.md
/docs/RENDER-GAP-VERIFICATION.md
/docs/NWIRO-HANDOFF.md
/docs/AGENT-HANDOFF.md
/docs/TOOL-SURFACE-OVERLOAD.md
/docs/NWIRO-TOOL-FILTERING-SPEC.md
/docs/NWIRO-TOOL-OBSERVABILITY-SPEC.md
/docs/M-1-INVESTIGATION-BRIEF.md
/docs/WAVE-1-IMPLEMENTATION-PLAN.md
/docs/WAVE-1-REVIEW.md
/docs/ROADMAP.md
/docs/COMPARISON-AND-ROADMAP.md
/docs/CONNECTOR-GAP-ANALYSIS.md
/docs/FINDINGS.md
/docs/M2-M6-TEST-RUNBOOK.md
/docs/M2-M6-V0.1.39-RETEST.md
/docs/VERIFY-GAP5-OPENROUTER.md

# Stray test-result archives (internal test logs). Never ship in a public repo.
/test/
*.zip
